all changes\n- `backend/web/routes/jwt_test.go` — step 8 amends existing test; steps 9–10 add two new tests\n\n## Verification\n1. `go test ./backend/web/routes/...` must pass.\n2. `go vet ./backend/...` must pass.\n3. Confirm new cross-token tests fail before fix is applied.\n\n## Decisions\n- Constants are unexported (`tokenTypeSession`, `tokenTypePreReg`) — they are an implementation detail of jwt.go.\n- `Typ` JSON key is `\"typ\"` in the payload (not JOSE header) — safe, library handles them separately.\n- `Typ` is exported on `JWTClaims` (needed for test assertions from the `_test` package).\n- Scope: jwt.go and jwt_test.go only. No middleware, no env vars, no new dependencies.\n"},"tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01XvZD6YyiPDxvv45ECHj6Jk__vscode-1773898184772","cwd":"/home/alexl70/src/pet/linkshortener"}

